videos.description: Golden Bears' Justice Sueing hits his 3rd three-pointer with a nice step-back jumper.
videos.headline: Cal's Sueing swishes 3-pointer

videos.description: Shockers' Landry Shamet sinks a 3-pointer on the wing, gets fouled on the play, and later makes the free throw.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Shamet with 4-point play

videos.description: Wichita State's  Landry Shamet sinks a 3-pointer on the wing, making him 4-4 on 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Shockers' Shamet drills another 3

videos.description: Cal's Dan Coleman dribbles around defenders while going in for the driving layup.
videos.headline: Coleman shows off handles

videos.description: Golden Bears' Don Coleman hits a 3-pointer, giving him 23 points for the game.
videos.headline: Cal's Coleman launches deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Landry Shamet gets a steal to spark a Wichita State comeback.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Shamet gets steal and dunk

videos.description: Marcus Lee gets back in transition and comes up with a huge block.
videos.headline: Cal's Lee pins it off the backboard

videos.description: Shaquille Morris gets the hoop and the harm to cut the Cal lead to two.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Morris gets the and-1

videos.description: Shaquille Morris' jumper puts Wichita State ahead of Cal for the first time since the first minute of the game.
videos.headline: Morris takes the lead for Wichita State
